{"id": "1402564599366029364", "channel_id": "1398340165482844302", "type": 19, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "Greetings, Keeper!\n\nTo clarify, the 0.5% Limited SSR rate in the Standard Banner works as follows:\n\nThe comprehensive SSR Awakener drop rate (including guarantee) is **5.00%** per pull.\nWhen you successfully pull an SSR, there is an **additional 10% chance (1/10) **for it to be a **Limited SSR**.\nThis results in an effective **0.5% overall chance per pull (5.00% × 10% = 0.5%) to obtain a Limited SSR**.\nWe appreciate your feedback, and our team is currently reviewing ways to improve the in-game descriptions to avoid confusion. Thank you for your support!", "timestamp": "2025-08-06T08:10:58.879000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["272394963642220545"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1402242456719720578", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398340165482844302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Clarification on gacha odds for standard limited", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
